        81, 
        'Witch Finder', 
        'C. L. Werner', 
        'SUMMARY:In this follow-up to "Witch Hunter," sinister agents of darkness plot the downfall of the civilized realms. To combat this insidious threat, the Old World draws upon the services of Mathias Thulman and the ruthless witch hunters to hunt down the evil within the land. Original.', 
