        82, 
        'Witch Hunter', 
        'C. L. Werner', 
        'SUMMARY:In the grim medieval Old World, the dreaded Witch Hunters hunt out evil throughout the towns, using whatever means they can to destroy those foolish enough to ally with the Dark Powers. Counted amongst the most zealous of the Witch Hunters is Marius Thurlman, a ruthless individual whose exploits are recounted in hopes of terrifying the citizens of the Empire. But can the brutal tales of burnings, fanatical trials, and torture really be true?', 
        '/uploads/36c7c294-3051-49b8-ac54-58f3f393cd90.jpg', 
