        'Christian Dunn, Marc Gascoigne', 
        'The galaxy is ablaze as war engulfs the Pyrus Reach Sector. The Pyrus Reach Sector is under attack from the vast hordes of Chaos, orks and eldar and it falls to the brave defenders of humanity to stem the tide. Featuring work from best-selling authors such as Dan Abnett and Graham McNeill, along with an array of hot new talent, this will appeal to players of Sabertooth Games'' collectible card game, SF readers and the legions of Games Workshop fans alike.', 
