    ) VALUES (
        183, 
        'Warrior Priest', 
        'Darius Hinks', 
        '(v1.0)
Product Description    Warrior Priest Jakob Wolff sets out to track down his brother, whose soul been tainted by the Ruinous Powers. Family must be put to one side as he battles to prevent the Empire from sinking into Chaos, with only his strength of arms and the purity of his beliefs to call upon.  About the AuthorAfter a music career so disastrous it landed him in court, Darius Hinks decided a job in publishing might be safer. His writing credits for the Black Library include The Witch Hunter’s Handbook, Warrior Priest and several short stories. Rumours that he still has a banjo hidden in his loft are fiercely refuted by his lawyers.', 
        '/uploads/e83e38f5-96c3-4580-878e-930a7c3869b8.jpg', 
