        410, 
        'Dragonslayer', 
        'William King', 
        'SUMMARY:Dragonslayer is the fourth epic instalment in the death-seeking saga of Gotrek and Felix. After the daring exploits in Daemonslayer, the fearless duo find themselves pursued by the insidious and ruthless skaven-lord, Grey Seer Thanquol. Drogonslayer sees the fearless Trollslayer and his sworn companion back aboard the arcane dwarf airship in search of a golden hoard - and its deadly guardian! New edition with stunning redesigned cover!', 
        '/uploads/b6091872-19c6-4c73-a1fd-f247b2821cc1.jpg', 
