        418, 
        'Shadowblood', 
        'William King', 
        'An army of undead monsters ravages the land.In order to overcome the sinister power behind them, Rik must master his birthright as a Shadowblood assassin under the tutelage of his deadliest enemy, his half-sister Tamara.', 
        '/uploads/2bd82370-5b7e-4b32-a990-7e9ad801809c.jpg', 
