    ) VALUES (
        426, 
        'Vampireslayer', 
        'William King', 
        'SUMMARY:In the unceasing war against Chaos, the doom-seeking dwarf Gotrek and his human companion Felix are beset by a new, terrible foe. An evil is forming in darkest Sylvania which threatens to reach out and tear the heart from our band of intrepid heroes. The gripping saga of Gotrek &amp; Felix continues in this epic tale of deadly battle and soul-rending tragedy.', 
        '/uploads/b9e9f24f-d570-40ef-9017-71273d46f1ea.jpg', 
